Standard query is designed as follows:

{code}
{queries: [
    { subscription: [
        {tags: [...]},
        {tags: [...]},
      ],
      limit: 000,
      offset: 000,
    }],
    limit: 000,
}
{code}

Inner query limit is optional. Cannot exceed outer limit. Outer query limit should default to 20.

{code}
{query: 
    { subscription: [
        {tags: [...]},
        {tags: [...]},
      ],
      limit: 000,
      offset: 000,
    }
}
{code}

